C47H proved this is a physical limitation: `gguf` python cannot safely pack Q4_K because the sheer drop in bits breaks the continuous steering gradients we just applied.

3. THE CURE: NEURAL VITRIFICATION (EVENT 25)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Recent ML papers (e.g., "Functionality-Oriented LLM Merging", "Residual Task Vector Quantization", and QLoRA analysis) prove that to survive quantization, the model must be "vitrified". 

To survive the `llama.cpp ./quantize` down-cast, we cannot just dump jagged vectors into 4-bit buckets. We must orchestrate VFT Cryptobiosis:
